description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars!

This pack includes the following content.

■Song Pack (10 songs)
・NAMCOT Medley
・KAGEKIYO " The Genji and the Heike Clans " Medley / From "The Genji and the Heike Clans"
・DRAGON SPIRIT Medley / From "DRAGON SPIRIT"
・Penetration of light into morality / From "RAY FORCE"
・ON THE VERGE OF REVIVAL(RED HARDCORE REMIX) / "Psychic Force" Arrangements
・Twister -Final Remix- / From "The World Ends with You -Final Remix-"
・Someday / From "The World Ends with You -Final Remix-"
・NEW GAME / From "NEO:The World Ends with You"
・LAST CALL / From "NEO:The World Ends with You"
・???(Secret)

■Navigator
・NEKU *with voice(CV:Koki Uchiyama)
・RINDO *with voice(CV:Yuma Uchida)

■Avatar
・R-GRAY0(3D)
・NEKU(2D)
・RINDO(2D)
・MINAMIMOTO(2D)
・SHOKA(2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: Game Song Pack
